    "body": "### Problem\n\n```\nERROR    test/functional/lua/net_spec.lua @ 19: vim.net.request fetches a URL into memory (async success)\ntest/functional/lua/net_spec.lua:36: attempt to index local 'content' (a userdata value)\n\nstack traceback:\n\ttest/functional/lua/net_spec.lua:36: in function <test/functional/lua/net_spec.lua:19>\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nx",
