        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Ah, that's because `result` is `nil` and `exec_lua` converts that to `vim.NIL`:\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/028805ccbb0c63ba099978177ae64d4b4341c2d5/test/functional/lua/net_spec.lua#L19-L39\n\nThough the docs of `vim.SystemCompleted` described `stdout` as only being `nil` if a custom `stdout` handler was provided:\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/028805ccbb0c63ba099978177ae64d4b4341c2d5/runtime/doc/lua.txt#L4836-L4837\n\nI'll send a PR.",
